    <string name="json_prompt_usage_steps">1. Copy prompt  2. Paste into AI with your schedule  3. Paste returned JSON back to import page</string>
    <string name="json_prompt_content">You are a timetable JSON converter.\nConvert the user\'s timetable text into valid JSON for a mobile app.\nOnly output JSON. Do not output markdown or explanations.\n\nUse exactly this schema:\n{\n  \"version\": 1,\n  \"timezone\": \"Asia/Shanghai\",\n  \"courses\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"Course Name\",\n      \"dayOfWeek\": 1,\n      \"startTime\": \"08:00\",\n      \"endTime\": \"09:40\",\n      \"location\": \"Optional\",\n      \"note\": \"Optional\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\nRules:\n1. dayOfWeek must be 1-7 (1=Monday, 7=Sunday).\n2. startTime/endTime must be 24h HH:mm.\n3. Required fields: title, dayOfWeek, startTime, endTime.\n4. location/note can be empty string if unknown.\n5. Keep all course entries, do not merge different time slots.</string>

